r omissions (function names, constants dropped) | `fingerprint.py` | V4-2 |\n    29→| Extraction-stage requirement loss (upstream guard) | `spec_structural_audit.py` | V1-C |\n    30→\n    31→Additionally, a prompt-level prevention layer reduces generation-time omissions:\n    32→\n    33→| Prevention Layer | Target | Source |\n    34→|---|---|---|\n    35→| Integration enumeration block in generate prompt | `prompts.py` | V1-D + V5-2 |\n...\n</persisted-output>"}]},"uuid":"e456f23b-032a-4d48-a4e5-239957afefcc","timestamp":"2026-03-17T18:46:59.849Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"d35e655b-f9c7-44b4-97d4-1f336a18d14a","userType":"external","cwd":"/config/workspace/IronClaude","sessionId":"caf57f20-b6f0-47d7-a404-b3840c9c44e5","version":"2.1.77","gitBranch":"v3.0-AuditGates","slug":"bright-juggling-reef"}
